column2: "Ah,<%me> looks like you came as well."
"Hehe, how do I look? Like a hunter?"
"Until Zeno comes back, I need to try harder to make up for his absence."
"I'm not fooling around or backing off, I came here to truly improve myself."
"I'm still not completely used to it, and I think I might get off course, but I intend to give it my all."
"Anyways, I wonder why there's a distress signal addressed to ARKS coming from this planet."
"I've looked high and low around here, but I haven't found anyone who looks like they called for help."
"It seems that the way time flows on this planet isn't normal ether. Something seems off."
"If we keep searching, we're bound to figure something out."
"Anyways, I'm going to get back to my quest. Bye bye."
